    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "July 28, 1964",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Mount Holly, New Jersey",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Dear Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "The object you saw was a bright meteor, sometimes",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "called a \"fireball\" or a \"bolide\". Almost all very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "bright meteors are small bodies moving in orbits rather",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "like the orbits of asteroids, and probably are fragments",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "of asteroids. The direction of motion of your meteor",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "is consistent with that sort of orbit. A good many",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "bright meteors strike the earth each day, but most go",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "unnoticed. We have received another report of the same",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "meteor from Wilmington, Delaware.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "I am sending your observation to the Moonwatch",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Division of the Smithsonian Astrophysical Observatory",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "here in Cambridge, which has a continuing program for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "analysis of visual observations of bright meteors.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Since it is very rarely possible for the professional",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "astronomer to observe these meteors, most of what is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "known about them depends on this sort of lucky chance.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
